                        <img alt="" class="adaptive-image" src="https://religiousstudies.yale.edu/sites/default/files/styles/adaptive/adaptive-image/public/gleaner_0.jpg?itok=X24fL5Y7" typeof="foaf:Image"/>
                       </li>
                      </ul>
